40 SEVERABILITY & EFFECTIVE DATE
41 SECTION 3.(a) If any provision of this act or the application thereof to any person
42 or circumstances is held invalid, such invalidity shall not affect other provisions or applications
43 of this act that can be given effect without the invalid provision or application and, to this end,
44 the provisions of this act are declared to be severable.
45 SECTION 3.(b) Effective Date. – Except as otherwise provided, this act is effective
46 when it becomes law.
